Zhao Pingan was born as his mother was killed in a car crash last year . 
  His mother was in labour when she and her husband were hit by a truck in Xiamen city . 
  Both parents were killed in the accident but the mother gave birth at the scene . 
  Pingan Zhao was 'catapulted' from his mother's womb and ended up ten feet away from her . 
  He was named China's 'miracle baby' and celebrated his first birthday on Saturday . 
 